high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the stove
Pick up a mug from the counter
Move to the microwave to the right of you
Heat the mug inside the microwave and retrieve it closing the door
Move to the coffee maker to the left of the sink
Place the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Go left and then right and stand in front of the toaster.
Pick the mug up from the counter.
Turn and go right to stand in front of the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and turn it on and then off and take the mug out and shut the door.
Go left and the left again and stand in front of the coffee maker.
Put the mug down under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed mug under a coffee maker.

high_descs: move left and locate the gas
pick up the mug from the gas
place the mug in the microwave to heat for sometime and then take it out
turn around towards the coffee maker
place the mug under the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a hot mug under a coffee maker
